hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: good material thanks generika fr panadol As the sun rose, people were already starting their day: barefoot women dressed in the brightest of prints walking with babies on backs and bundles on heads, policemen waiting at bus stops for a free lift in the very same vehicle they would probably fine at a roadblock later in the day, young men on bicycles wearing improbably warm hats, and tiny children arranging their stock of half a dozen watermelons into pyramids, to create the most eye-catching display of all.
